SAVEFL   TITLE 'PLI CALLABLE ROUTINE TO SAVE CONTENTS OF ARRAYS'        SAV00010*                                                                       SAV00020*                                                                       SAV00030*                                                                     * SAV00040* CALLING SEQUENCE:                                                   * SAV00050*                                                                     * SAV00060* SAVEFL (FILENAME, FILETYPE, FILEMODE,             CHAR(8)           * SAV00070*         ARRAY1, LENGTH_ARRAY1,                                      * SAV00080*         ARRAY2, LENGTH_ARRAY2,                                      * SAV00090*         ARRAY3, LENGTH_ARRAY3,                                      * SAV00100*         ARRAY4, LENGTH_ARRAY4,                                      * SAV00110*         ARRAY5, LENGTH_ARRAY5,                                      * SAV00120*         ARRAY6, LENGTH_ARRAY6,                                      * SAV00130*         ARRAY7, LENGTH_ARRAY7,                                      * SAV00140*         ARRAY8, LENGTH_ARRAY8,                                      * SAV00150*                               RTN_CODE)                             * SAV00160*   RETURN CODES:    0   IF  ALL OK                                   * SAV00170*                    1   IF FILE EXISTS ALREADY                       * SAV00180*                 2-27   FROM FSWRITE MACRO                           * SAV00190*                   36   DISK NOT ACCESSED                            * SAV00200SAVEFL   CSECT ,                                                        SAV00210         SAVE  (14,12),,*                                               SAV00220         LR    R12,R15                                                  SAV00230         USING SAVEFL,R12                                               SAV00240*********************************************************************** SAV00250